title: Ophthalmology library - Tensai 2013 - Version 2
description:
THIS IS THE SECOND VERSION OF THE RELEASE, FIRST VERSION HAD SOME CORRUPTED FILES.

These books are most of the Ophthalmology books available on the internet for free. 

This is the start of an ophthalmology collection, firstly started by Tenuki and with some additions from users all over the internet. In fact, it's a package extracted from a Facebook group which has recently become non-free.

For all the users who, as myself, joined the old Emedicina.biz and enjoyed the Okdokey collection. This is for you ;)


Sharing speed will be low during the first days. Be patient

This package includes the most important ophthalmology books: Kanski, Yanoff, Ryan, Gass, Shields, the american academy books, Krachmer...
